{% block content %}
    <p>Hi {{ name }},</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 30px">
        Last week, we asked you to activate your membership by confirming your email address. We think this might have slipped your mind, but don’t worry – it’s not too late!<br> 
        Complete it with just one click:
    </p>
