    <p><u>Need help?</u></p>
    <p>If you have any questions or run into any issues, feel free to contact us at <a style="color: #fac000;" href="mailto:hi@hiflanders.be">hi@hiflanders.be</a> or call <a style="color: #fac000;" href="tel:+3232327218">+32 3 232 72 18</a> during office hours.</p>
    <p>Looking forward to welcoming you to one of our hostels soon!</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px">Warm regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The Hi Flanders Team</strong></p>
{% endblock %}